# Artifacts generated when the tutorial is run.
#
# SWE ladder (notebooks 04-09):
notebooks/build/
notebooks/CMakeLists.txt
notebooks/swe_step.cpython-*.so
notebooks/timings.json

# Kernel / asynchrony notebooks (10-12): %%writefile scripts, Nsight
# profiler reports, the downloaded text corpus, and rendered plots.
# Patterns are applied at the notebooks/ root and under solutions/, since
# executing the solution notebooks (e.g. in CI) writes the same artifacts there.
notebooks/*.py
notebooks/solutions/*.py
!notebooks/swe_core.py
notebooks/*.nsys-rep
notebooks/solutions/*.nsys-rep
notebooks/*.sqlite
notebooks/solutions/*.sqlite
notebooks/*.ncu-rep
notebooks/solutions/*.ncu-rep
notebooks/books__15m.txt
notebooks/solutions/books__15m.txt
notebooks/test.png
notebooks/solutions/test.png

# Generated C/C++ from %%writefile cells (nanobind / cffi / cppjit / interop
# exercises). The checked-in tutorial source is re-included below.
notebooks/solutions/*.c
notebooks/solutions/*.cpp
notebooks/solutions/*.cxx
notebooks/solutions/*.hpp
notebooks/solutions/*.hxx
!notebooks/solutions/swe_step.cpp
!notebooks/solutions/swe_thrust_solver.cpp

__pycache__/
*.egg-info/
*.log
